#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you select the <guilabel>Use default port</guilabel> checkbox, then "
#| "&krfb; will locate a suitable port, and invitations will match this port. "
#| "If you deselect this checkbox, you can specify a particular port. "
#| "Specifying a particular port may be useful if you are using port-"
